		<td width="150" align="left" valign="top" class="row1"><span class="name"><a name="45666"></a><b>Istaril</b></span><br /><span class="postdetails">The World's Most Arrogant Mage<br /><img src="images/avatars/6459610573e810e07eb682.jpg" alt="" border="0" /><br /><br />Joined: 10 Mar 2003<br />Posts: 432<br />Location: Granada, Spain</span><br /></td>
