				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Easy answer is to make it a *MAGE* pet.
<br />

<br />
It wont waste time on Snares or roots!
<br />

<br />
If it was made to cast as say a lvl 52/53 mage, as it currently on test is a lvl 52/53 wizard, its spells would be:
<br />

<br />
Char, 700 hp fire DD, DPs 155
<br />
Shock of Swords, 600 hp magic DD, DPs 98.3
<br />
Malosi for debuff
<br />

<br />
Mage NPCs don't cast root/snare, make it so that it doesn't cast pets (note many NPC mages don't cast pets). You take time wasting bad/not wanted spells right out of the equation!<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=304331" target="_blank" class="postlink"><span style="font-weight: bold"><span style="color: red">REDORIOUS.....ARCHMAGE.....KARANA</span></span></a>
